test directly on our platform.

00:15:00.050 --> 00:15:01.800
MILENA NIKOLIC: We
want you to experiment,

00:15:01.800 --> 00:15:05.040
we want you to iterate, and
we want you to do this fast.

00:15:05.040 --> 00:15:07.470
This is why I'm happy to
announce that last week,

00:15:07.470 --> 00:15:10.600
we launched multiple concurrent
localized Store Listing

00:15:10.600 --> 00:15:11.580
Experiments.

00:15:11.580 --> 00:15:14.500
We want you to go globally
faster and have better tools

00:15:14.500 --> 00:15:17.360
to test localized versions
of your Store listing.

00:15:17.360 --> 00:15:19.430
You can now run up
to five Experiments

00:15:19.430 --> 00:15:22.357
with different languages
at the same time.

00:15:22.357 --> 00:15:23.190
KOBI GLICK: Awesome.

00:15:23.190 --> 00:15:25.390
So you're talking about
making things faster, right?

00:15:25.390 --> 00:15:25.640
MILENA NIKOLIC: Indeed.

00:15:25.640 --> 00:15:26.510
KOBI GLICK: One
thing that is not

00:15:26.510 --> 00:15:28.635
fast today is making price
changes in the Developer

00:15:28.635 --> 00:15:29.190
Console.

00:15:29.190 --> 00:15:31.460
This really sucks, actually.

00:15:31.460 --> 00:15:33.380
Because lots of people
have the same price

00:15:33.380 --> 00:15:35.857
point to many in-app
products or paid apps.

00:15:35.857 --> 00:15:37.440
So what are we going
to do about that?

00:15:37.440 --> 00:15:40.130
MILENA NIKOLIC: I'm very
glad you asked, Kobi.

00:15:40.130 --> 00:15:41.750
We want to make
this faster as well.

00:15:41.750 --> 00:15:43.720
We want to make
pricing faster as well.

00:15:43.720 --> 00:15:46.390
So I'm also happy to announce
that earlier this week,

00:15:46.390 --> 00:15:49.050
we have launched
Pricing Templates.

00:15:49.050 --> 00:15:51.670
With Pricing Templates,
you can define prices

00:15:51.670 --> 00:15:54.320
across all of the markets
that Google Play supports.

00:15:54.320 --> 00:15:57.570
Did you guys know that there
are 70 such markets now?

00:15:57.570 --> 00:15:58.920
Yeah.

00:15:58.920 --> 00:16:01.090
Once you create a
template, you can link it

00:16:01.090 --> 00:16:04.882
to as many paid apps or
in-app products as you want.

00:16:04.882 --> 00:16:06.340
If you make a change
to a template,

00:16:06.340 --> 00:16:09.550
it gets propagated
to all of the apps.

00:16:09.550 --> 00:16:11.790
So, for example, if you're
like Toca Boca Games

00:16:11.790 --> 00:16:15.811
and selling multiple titles
at, let's say, $2.99,

00:16:15.811 --> 00:16:18.570
you only need to make changes
to your template once,

00:16:18.570 --> 00:16:21.230
and it will be propagated
to all of your apps.

00:16:21.230 --> 00:16:24.000
If you're like Wooga,
selling in-app products

00:16:24.000 --> 00:16:27.060
at multiple price points,
for example, $1.99, $4.99,

00:16:27.060 --> 00:16:31.350
and $9.99, you only need
to maintain three templates

00:16:31.350 --> 00:16:32.980
instead of manually
making changes

00:16:32.980 --> 00:16:35.390
to tens or hundreds
of individual pricing

00:16:35.390 --> 00:16:37.860
points in multiple
different currencies.

00:16:37.860 --> 00:16:39.740
Like in this feedback
we got from Toca Boca,

00:16:39.740 --> 00:16:42.500
we hope Pricing Templates
will help you move faster

00:16:42.500 --> 00:16:45.526
and get successful.

00:16:45.526 --> 00:16:46.150
KOBI GLICK: OK.

00:16:46.150 --> 00:16:48.340
So it's important
for us you're also

00:16:48.340 --> 00:16:50.530
able to localize
your price better.

00:16:50.530 --> 00:16:53.500
This is why we also
launched Round Pricing.

00:16:53.500 --> 00:16:56.950
With Round Pricing, we're
not, like we used to do,

00:16:56.950 --> 00:16:59.800
just converting the price
using today's exchange rate.

00:16:59.800 --> 00:17:03.350
We also apply locally relevant,
country-specific rounding

00:17:03.350 --> 00:17:03.980
rules.

00:17:03.980 --> 00:17:08.550
So a price like 9.73
euros becomes 9.99 euros.

00:17:08.550 --> 00:17:11.599
A price like 196
Japanese yen simply

00:17:11.599 --> 00:17:13.250
becomes 200 Japanese yen.

00:17:13.250 --> 00:17:17.040
And 25,235 Indonesian
rupee simply

00:17:17.040 --> 00:17:20.650
becomes 25,000 Indonesian rupee.

00:17:20.650 --> 00:17:23.369
We are sure that this change,
like the feedback you see here

00:17:23.369 --> 00:17:25.810
from Wooga, will help you
streamline your pricing

00:17:25.810 --> 00:17:30.250
structures and make your
businesses even better.

00:17:30.250 --> 00:17:32.940
Now, while we're helping you
make price changes faster

00:17:32.940 --> 00:17:35.830
with templates and more
locally relevant with rounding,

00:17:35.830 --> 00:17:38.820
we're keeping your ability
to tweak the prices manually

00:17:38.820 --> 00:17:39.877
in the Developer Console.

00:17:39.877 --> 00:17:41.460
We know that this
is important for you

00:17:41.460 --> 00:17:43.160
when you run a
short-time promotion

00:17:43.160 --> 00:17:46.200
or try new pricing strategies.

00:17:46.200 --> 00:17:48.890
We are sure that the new
changes we are making to pricing

00:17:48.890 --> 00:17:52.719
will help you go
globally faster.

00:17:52.719 --> 00:17:53.510
MILENA NIKOLIC: OK.

