time-critical changes wherever

00:18:14.460 --> 00:18:15.350
you are.

00:18:15.350 --> 00:18:16.840
When you're rapidly
iterating, you

00:18:16.840 --> 00:18:20.150
need a power tool that's in
your pocket at all times,

00:18:20.150 --> 00:18:23.030
and we've built Play Console
app exactly with those use cases

00:18:23.030 --> 00:18:23.940
