00:18:23.940 --> 00:18:26.080
Whether you want to quickly
reply to a user review

00:18:26.080 --> 00:18:30.350
or show off performance of your
app to a venture capitalist,

00:18:30.350 --> 00:18:33.250
Play Console app should
be there to support you.

