You can also track
your crash reports,

00:18:45.270 --> 00:18:48.520
including hourly data
and full stack traces.

00:18:48.520 --> 00:18:51.130
You can also see ratings
and user reviews,

00:18:51.130 --> 00:18:52.940
and you can reply
to user reviews.

00:18:52.940 --> 00:18:54.990
You can also track the
state of your release.

00:18:54.990 --> 00:18:56.570
For example, is it
in beta testing,

00:18:56.570 --> 00:18:59.622
is it in staged rollout,
or has it reached prod yet?

