Out of that huge
audience, we want

00:22:31.960 --> 00:22:34.702
to help you find the
best users for your app.

00:22:37.380 --> 00:22:39.077
So that's why you're all here.

00:22:39.077 --> 00:22:40.660
Today, we're going
to walk through how

00:22:40.660 --> 00:22:43.390
we can work together to improve
app discovery in the Play

00:22:43.390 --> 00:22:44.479
Store.

00:22:44.479 --> 00:22:46.020
There are a lot of
important elements

00:22:46.020 --> 00:22:48.020
that contribute to
discovery, and some of which

00:22:48.020 --> 00:22:49.802
you've already heard about.

00:22:49.802 --> 00:22:51.510
But we're going to
touch on a few of them

00:22:51.510 --> 00:22:53.305
again, because
they're that important

00:22:53.305 --> 00:22:56.364
and because they directly
contribute to discovery.

00:22:56.364 --> 00:22:58.280
We've narrowed them down
to the most critical,

00:22:58.280 --> 00:23:00.650
and we're going to go
through each of them--

00:23:00.650 --> 00:23:04.390
build something great,
listen to your users,

00:23:04.390 --> 00:23:07.137
optimize your presence,
and expand your reach.

00:23:09.760 --> 00:23:12.090
And then we're going to
share some insights about how

00:23:12.090 --> 00:23:13.970
the discovery
mechanisms in the Store

00:23:13.970 --> 00:23:17.377
actually work, some of which
we've never shared before.

