00:28:33.960 --> 00:28:35.870
are finding the most success.

00:28:35.870 --> 00:28:39.460
They continue to test
and refine and understand

00:28:39.460 --> 00:28:40.940
user preferences.

00:28:40.940 --> 00:28:43.080
Ultimately, Rovio saw
significant uplift

00:28:43.080 --> 00:28:45.680
as a result of
their Experiments.

00:28:45.680 --> 00:28:47.450
And back to discovery.

00:28:47.450 --> 00:28:50.796
Higher conversion rates from
your listing to installs

00:28:50.796 --> 00:28:52.170
are an important
signal, and they

00:28:52.170 --> 00:28:55.000
help us understand when
a user has successfully

00:28:55.000 --> 00:28:57.602
gone from searching for
an app to finding one

00:28:57.602 --> 00:28:58.810
that they think they'll love.

00:29:01.750 --> 00:29:03.280
So now, you've
built a great app,

00:29:03.280 --> 00:29:05.210
you've implemented
important feedback,

00:29:05.210 --> 00:29:07.360
and you have a strong
Play Store presence.

00:29:07.360 --> 00:29:09.036
What's next?

00:29:09.036 --> 00:29:10.410
There are different
opportunities

00:29:10.410 --> 00:29:12.720
to expand your reach,
depending on the type of app

00:29:12.720 --> 00:29:15.170
you have and the type of
experiences that your users

00:29:15.170 --> 00:29:17.780
are looking for.

00:29:17.780 --> 00:29:20.460
Going global and finding
audiences in new markets

00:29:20.460 --> 00:29:22.270
is a strategy that's
worked extremely well

00:29:22.270 --> 00:29:24.100
for many developers,
so we're going

00:29:24.100 --> 00:29:27.000
to explore a few tips and tools
that can help you find success

00:29:27.000 --> 00:29:27.655
in new markets.

00:29:30.510 --> 00:29:33.782
So earlier, we talked about
the massive reach of Android.

00:29:33.782 --> 00:29:35.490
We've actually looked
at the growth rates

00:29:35.490 --> 00:29:37.580
of apps that are
available globally

00:29:37.580 --> 00:29:41.590
and those that are only
available in specific markets.

00:29:41.590 --> 00:29:46.730
Global apps grew 2.4 times
faster than non-global apps.

00:29:46.730 --> 00:29:48.319
Now, this makes intuitive sense.

00:29:48.319 --> 00:29:50.610
If you have more markets,
you have a larger addressable

00:29:50.610 --> 00:29:51.514
audience.

00:29:51.514 --> 00:29:52.930
But the data really
proves it out.

00:29:56.020 --> 00:29:58.510
There are a few specific
things to consider when you're

00:29:58.510 --> 00:30:00.380
planning to localize your app.

00:30:00.380 --> 00:30:02.630
First, you should use
the Dev Console reports

00:30:02.630 --> 00:30:05.110
that we talked about to
understand where new user

00:30:05.110 --> 00:30:10.460
bases are growing and prioritize
localizing for those markets.

00:30:10.460 --> 00:30:14.324
Second, don't just
translate, actually localize.

00:30:14.324 --> 00:30:15.990
This means ensure
that you're culturally

00:30:15.990 --> 00:30:18.210
aware of local
market expectations

00:30:18.210 --> 00:30:20.810
and be ready to
support your new users.

00:30:20.810 --> 00:30:23.600
Last, always be prepared
to test and iterate.

00:30:23.600 --> 00:30:25.385
New users means new feedback.

00:30:27.900 --> 00:30:31.940
A developer who did incredibly
well with this is 1Password.

00:30:31.940 --> 00:30:35.060
They localized their Store
description, their screenshots,

00:30:35.060 --> 00:30:38.240
the content, and the
messaging inside their app.

00:30:38.240 --> 00:30:40.560
And we looked at those
signals to understand

00:30:40.560 --> 00:30:43.180
when the app was ready to
be shown to local users.

00:30:43.180 --> 00:30:45.740
For 1Password, the
investment really paid off.

00:30:48.290 --> 00:30:51.710
After two weeks of work,
they saw 100x install growth

00:30:51.710 --> 00:30:52.990
in Korea.

00:30:52.990 --> 00:30:55.110
It was really pretty incredible.

00:30:55.110 --> 00:30:57.410
By focusing on
local market users,

00:30:57.410 --> 00:30:58.690
they made a real difference.

00:30:58.690 --> 00:31:01.330
And in most cases,
it's worth the effort

00:31:01.330 --> 00:31:04.760
if your plan is to grow
through market expansion.

00:31:04.760 --> 00:31:07.800
And we have powerful tools to
help, like the localization

00:31:07.800 --> 00:31:10.610
checklist, access to
translation services,

00:31:10.610 --> 00:31:12.526
and the new pricing
features that Kobi shared.

00:31:15.300 --> 00:31:17.460
So we've reviewed the
most important ways

00:31:17.460 --> 00:31:19.790
that you can directly
affect the discoverability

00:31:19.790 --> 00:31:24.400
of your app and some key actions
that you can take right away.

00:31:24.400 --> 00:31:26.950
For build something
great, limit permissions,

00:31:26.950 --> 00:31:29.270
and focus on beautiful design.

00:31:29.270 --> 00:31:30.680
Listen to your users.

00:31:30.680 --> 00:31:32.090
Feedback is a gift.

00:31:32.090 --> 00:31:34.120
Use it to get better.

00:31:34.120 --> 00:31:35.680
Optimize your presence.

00:31:35.680 --> 00:31:38.510
Experiment your way to
improve conversions.

00:31:38.510 --> 00:31:39.860
And expand your reach.

00:31:39.860 --> 00:31:41.234
Go global and localize.

