Android's design principles.

00:37:32.770 --> 00:37:34.700
Does your app measure up?

00:37:34.700 --> 00:37:36.770
Two, for listening
to your users,

00:37:36.770 --> 00:37:41.030
we recommend addressing user
feedback, especially when it

00:37:41.030 --> 00:37:42.010
