00:37:42.010 --> 00:37:44.040
Squash those bugs.

00:37:44.040 --> 00:37:47.380
Number three, for
optimizing your presence,

00:37:47.380 --> 00:37:50.110
why not try a Store
Listing Experiment?

00:37:50.110 --> 00:37:53.160
And finally, number four,
for expanding your reach,

00:37:53.160 --> 00:37:55.320
we recommend reviewing
the market report

00:37:55.320 --> 00:37:56.434
in the Developer Console.

